.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/c8/China_Schweinestall_Linden-Museum.jpg/300px-China_Schweinestall_Linden-Museum.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2Fc%2Fc8%2FChina_Schweinestall_Linden-Museum.jpg%2F300px-China_Schweinestall_Linden-Museum.jpg&h=f49af500&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n依種做法有三個好處<br />\n1. 將廁所同豬圈放埋一齊 減少左污染源<br />\n2. 人畜糞合一 方便使用。 點用呀？用黎做肥料 果陣未有孟都山嘅化學肥料 依d就係最好嘅農業肥料<br />\n3. 廁所起係豬圈上面 慳左好多地方<br />\n<br />\n而缺點大家都估到 就係容易傳播寄生蟲病"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T09:54:53.000Z","msg":"印度好似都有類似，屎塔下面係豬圈，下面d豬有時會探個頭出黎，所有會有碌棍比你打走隻豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc82bf59656714b61f80a72c87503b0e24acdc4c","tid":2489692,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"706b7a5ed18856adcca81b0abc7ce4614fd3ae21","tid":2489692,"uid":34222,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T09:47:29.000Z","msg":"先秦時候D諸侯去廁所其實幾危險<br />\n好似《史記．刺客列傳》載豫讓扮成刑人係宮中洗廁所，想刺殺趙襄子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可想而知去廁所隨時有生命安危"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T09:56:31.000Z","msg":"同時古廁所亦係成就大事嘅關鍵地點之始<br />\n<br />\n東漢劉志 漢恒帝 就係喺廁所 同佢個大將軍衛青開會 夾埋幾個太監 成功殺鳩左當時權傾朝野嘅外戚梁冀 重奪政權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  不過亦都造就左宦官亂政"},{"pid":"b8294aa245c53791de6c9470946ffd6294e559ec","tid":2489692,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9be3e7aa1e951fc9014a64d81690f17e3e065817","tid":2489692,"uid":120935,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"60353dc2cdf9c4ab8d59b58548627452c0a53e83","tid":2489692,"uid":14103,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:06:05.000Z","msg":"去到漢代 就通常會起係後園度 仲會起高一層 上面屙 下面就豬圈 我地屙出黎嘅屎屎就直接俾豬食 叫「圂廁」<br />\nWiki中圂廁示意圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/c8